{{DISPLAYTITLE:VDW_ALPHA}}
{{TAGDEF|VDW_ALPHA|[real (array)]}}

Description: {{TAG|VDW_ALPHA}} defines the polarizability <math>\alpha_{0}</math> (bohr<math>^{3}</math>) for each species defined in the {{TAG|POSCAR}} file.
----
{{TAG|VDW_ALPHA}} sets the polarizability <math>\alpha_{0}</math> (bohr<math>^{3}</math>) for each species defined in the {{TAG|POSCAR}} file for the [[Tkatchenko-Scheffler_method|Tkatchenko-Scheffler]] and [[Many-body dispersion energy|Many-body dispersion energy]] methods.

